Description_lang: Summons an Ancient Tempest centered around a Stormwraith in the Eye of the Storm. The Tempest pushes players away from the Eye of the Storm and inflicts $295921s1 Frost damage every $295920t1 sec. This Frost damage inflicted increases as the storm persists. Also reduces damage taken by Radiance of Azshara by $s3%.While the Tempest is active, Stormlings will continually spawn within the Eye of the Storm.When the Stormwraith is defeated, the Tempest recedes.
